EXEC sp_rename 'Temp1','GTT0404'

truncate table GTT0404_BI

Insert Into
GTT0404_BI(date,FlowType,Year,Month,Reporter,Partner,Code,FourDigit,SixDigit,Item,Commodity,
Class,Volume,Unit,Value,Currency,lb,normval,normlbs,MOMPerc,MOMActualLbs,MOMNormLbs,
YOYPerc,YOYActualLbs,YOYNormLbs,YTDPerc,YTDActualLbs,YTDNormLbs,Avg5Year,Avg5YearVol)

select GTT0404.Date, GTT0404.FlowType, GTT0404.Year, GTT0404.Month,
GTT0404.Declarant, GTT0404.Partner, GTT0404.Code,ItemTable.FourDigit,ItemTable.SixDigit,
GTT0404.item,CommodityTable.Commodity,ClassTable.Class, GTT0404.Volume, GTT0404.Unit, GTT0404.Value,
GTT0404.Currency, GTT0404.LB, GTT0404.NormVal, GTT0404.Normlbs, GTT0404.MOMPerc,
GTT0404.MOMActualLbs,MOMNormLbs, GTT0404.YOYPerc, GTT0404.YOYActualLbs, GTT0404.YOYNormLbs,
GTT0404.YTDperc, GTT0404.YTDActualLbs, GTT0404.YTDNormLbs, GTT0404.Avg5Year,
GTT0404.Avg5YearVol 

From 

GTT0404 Inner Join ItemTable on GTT0404.Code = ItemTable.TradeCode 
Inner Join CommodityTable on ItemTable.Commodity = CommodityTable.CommodityID
Inner Join ClassTable on ItemTable.Class = ClassTable.ClassID
